== 搜救 ==
空难当日，科摩罗副总统宣布飞机残骸已经找到，并发现有遇难者的遗体和许多碎片在科摩罗群岛海域漂浮<ref name="CNN" />。初步调查显示，这些遗体和碎片在距莫罗尼国际机场16至17公里的海面上<ref name="XINHUA">[http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2009-06/30/content_11627093.htm   本网连线：科摩罗海域发现遇难者遗体] {{Wayback|url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2009-06/30/content_11627093.htm |date=20100130082942 }}，新华网</ref>。科摩罗警方称，该国缺乏海上搜救能力<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2009/06/30/world/africa/30yemen.html |work=The New York Times |title=Jet Goes Down in Indian Ocean With 153 Aboard |accessdate=2009-07-01 |date=2009-06-30 |archive-date=2020-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109034334/http://www.nytimes.com/2009/06/30/world/africa/30yemen.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。经过搜救，在近海救起1名12岁法国籍女童（這名女童随即被带上海岸并送往医院）<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.sina.com.cn/w/2009-07-01/075718129477.shtml |title=也门航班空难12岁女孩生还 新浪网 |accessdate=2009-07-01 |archive-date=2018-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181108144448/http://news.sina.com.cn/w/2009-07-01/075718129477.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2009-07/01/content_11632111.htm |title=一名14岁法国少女在也航空难中幸存 新华网. 12岁的女孩在一些碎片漂浮在大海中约13个小时，完全赤裸，没有救生衣。 |accessdate=2009-07-01 |archive-date=2017-02-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170212222824/http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2009-07/01/content_11632111.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，此前的消息一度认为找到的是一名5岁的女童. 唯一的幸存者是一名12岁的女孩。该女童被发现了在一块飞机碎片上漂浮。她全身赤裸。<ref name="CNN2">[http://edition.cnn.com/2009/WORLD/meast/06/30/yemen.plane.crash/index.html  Child found alive after plane crashes in sea] {{Wayback|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2009/WORLD/meast/06/30/yemen.plane.crash/index.html |date=20201109040359 }}，CNN</ref><ref>[http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2009-06/30/content_11628310.htm 一名也航失事客机上的生还者获救] {{Wayback|url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2009-06/30/content_11628310.htm |date=20160613170711 }}，新华网14岁的女孩在一些碎片漂浮在大海中约13个小时，完全赤裸，没有救生衣。</ref>。目前已找到11具遇难者的遗体<ref name="XINHUA2" />。 

两架[[法國軍事|法国军队]]的飞机和一艘船已开始搜索航班的幸存者<ref name=bbc>{{Cite web|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/africa/8125664.stm|title=Yemen jet crashes in Indian Ocean|publisher=BBC News|accessdate=2009-07-01|date=2009-06-30|archive-date=2018-07-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180723193743/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/africa/8125664.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，它们都是从[[留尼旺岛|留尼旺岛]]和[[马约特岛|马约特岛]]派来的<ref name="france24">{{Cite web|title=Bodies 'found' from crashed Yemeni airliner|url=http://www.france24.com/en/20090630-yemeni-airways-wreckage-bodies-spotted-comoros-airbus-iy626|publisher=France 24|accessdate=2009-07-01|date=2009-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090703065038/http://www.france24.com/en/20090630-yemeni-airways-wreckage-bodies-spotted-comoros-airbus-iy626|archive-date=2009-07-03|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

法国官方称，其中一个[[飞行记录器|飛航資料記錄器]]在7月1日已被找到，马上就能修复。<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/africa/8127947.stm |publisher = BBC News |title = Yemen plane's black box located |accessdate = 2009-07-01 |date = 2009-07-01 |archive-date = 2020-11-09 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201109035915/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/africa/8127947.stm |dead-url = no }}</ref>

